#. Macedonian sky culture authors section in markdown format
msgid ""
"This sky culture was contributed by *Vancho Stojkoski* and *Gjore Cenev* "
"from Macedonian Research Society based primarily on the book **Sky over "
"Macedonia** by Cenev G, 2004."
msgstr ""
"这种星空文化是由马其顿研究学会的 *Vancho Stojkoski*和*Gjore Cenev*贡献的，主要以*马其顿的天空*(Sky over "
"Macedonia, Cenev G, 2004)为基础。 <p>中文翻译：Sun Shuwei"

#. Maori sky culture name
msgid "Maori"
msgstr "毛利"

#. Maori sky culture introduction section in markdown format
msgid ""
"The Maori (New Zealand) night sky is similar to the Polynesian night sky. "
"But it differs enough to warrant its own sky culture. Maritime themes are "
"central to the Maori sky culture and were used extensively in nautical "
"navigation. Along with most other cultures, the rising and setting of "
"prominent stars were used to signal planting and harvesting seasons."
msgstr ""
"毛利人（新西兰）的夜空与波利尼西亚地区的夜空相似，但其独特之处足以构成独立的星空文化。海洋主题在毛利星空文化中占据核心地位，并被广泛应用于航海导航。与其他多数文化一样，毛利人也通过观测显著星辰的升落来判断播种与收获的时节。"

#. Maori sky culture description section in markdown format
msgid ""
"### Taatai-arorangi-maori\n"
"\n"
"There are tribal ('iwi') variations in the naming of the stars and constellations. The names referenced below are the more well known names.\n"
"\n"
"   |Object|Name|\n"
"   |--------|------|\n"
"   |Mercury|Takero|\n"
"   |Venus (morning star)|Tawera|\n"
"   |Venus (evening star)|Meremere|\n"
"   |Mars|Rangiwhenua|\n"
"   |Jupiter|Perearau|\n"
"   |Saturn|Perearau (Both Jupiter and Saturn have the same name)|\n"
"   |Altair|Poutu-te-Rangi|\n"
"   |Antares|Rehua|\n"
"   |S_Sco|Pekehawani|\n"
"   |T_Sco|Whakaonge-kai|\n"
"   |Canopus|Autahi|\n"
"   |Procyon|Puanga Hori|\n"
"   |Rigel|Puanga|\n"
"   |Sirius|Takarua|\n"
"   |Vega|Whanui|\n"
"   |Spica|Whiti-Kapeka or Mariao|\n"
"   |Arcturus|Ruawahia|\n"
"   |Castor|Whakaahu|\n"
"   |Pollux|Whakaahu (Both Castor and Pollux have the same name)|\n"
"   |Aldebaran|Taumatakuku|\n"
"   |Achernar|Turu|\n"
"   |Orion (whole belt)|Hao - o- rua|\n"
"   |Orion (the belt)|Tau toro|\n"
"   |Orion (a part)|Te Kakau|\n"
"   |Scorpio|Ruhi|\n"
"   |Scorpio (the tail)|Te Waka-o-Tama-Rereti|\n"
"   |Pleiades|Matariki|\n"
"   |Stars in the Pleiades (unspecified):|Tupua-nuku, Tupua-rangi, Ururangi, Wai-puna-a-rangi, Waiti, Waita|\n"
"   |Pointers|Te Taura Ra o Tainui|\n"
"   |Hyades|Te Kokota|\n"
"   |Southern Cross|Mahutonga|\n"
"   |Coal sack|Te Patiki|\n"
"   |Milky Way|Te ika o te rangi|\n"
"   |Large Magellanic cloud|Te Waka Ruru|\n"
"   |Small Magellanic cloud|Tuputuputu|\n"
"   |Double stars|Pipiri|\n"
"   |Comets|Auihi Turoa|\n"
"   |Ecliptic|Pito - o - Watea|\n"
"   |Moon|Te Marama|\n"
"   |Sun|Te Ra|\n"
"   |Te-Ra-o-Tainui|A maori constellation without a European counterpart. It is a sea voyaging catamaran. The belt of orion is the keel, the hyades is a claw sail and the Pleiades is the bow.|"
msgstr ""
"### 毛利星空文化（Taatai-arorangi-maori）\n"
"\n"
"各部落（“iwi”）对星辰与星座的命名存在差异，下表所列名称为较广为人知的版本。\n"
"\n"
"| 天体/星座 | 毛利名称 |\n"
"|------------------|----------------------------------|\n"
"| 水星 | Takero |\n"
"| 金星（晨星） | Tawera |\n"
"| 金星（昏星） | Meremere |\n"
"| 火星 | Rangiwhenua |\n"
"| 木星 | Perearau |\n"
"| 土星 | Perearau（木星与土星同名） |\n"
"| 河鼓二（牛郎星） | Poutu-te-Rangi |\n"
"| 心宿二（天蝎座α）| Rehua |\n"
"| 天蝎座σ星 | Pekehawani |\n"
"| 天蝎座τ星 | Whakaonge-kai |\n"
"| 老人星 | Autahi |\n"
"| 南河三 | Puanga Hori |\n"
"| 参宿七 | Puanga |\n"
"| 天狼星 | Takarua |\n"
"| 织女星 | Whanui |\n"
"| 角宿一 | Whiti-Kapeka 或 Mariao |\n"
"| 大角星 | Ruawahia |\n"
"| 北河二（双子座α）| Whakaahu |\n"
"| 北河三（双子座β）| Whakaahu（北河二与北河三同名） |\n"
"| 毕宿五 | Taumatakuku |\n"
"| 水委一 | Turu |\n"
"| 猎户座（整条腰带）| Hao-o-rua |\n"
"| 猎户座腰带 | Tau toro |\n"
"| 猎户座（部分） | Te Kakau |\n"
"| 天蝎座 | Ruhi |\n"
"| 天蝎座尾部 | Te Waka-o-Tama-Rereti |\n"
"| 昴星团 | Matariki |\n"
"| 昴星团诸星（未特指）| Tupua-nuku, Tupua-rangi, Ururangi, Wai-puna-a-rangi, Waiti, Waita |\n"
"| 南十字座指极星 | Te Taura Ra o Tainui |\n"
"| 毕星团 | Te Kokota |\n"
"| 南十字座 | Mahutonga |\n"
"| 煤袋星云 | Te Patiki |\n"
"| 银河 | Te ika o te rangi |\n"
"| 大麦哲伦云 | Te Waka Ruru |\n"
"| 小麦哲伦云 | Tuputuputu |\n"
"| 双星 | Pipiri |\n"
"| 彗星 | Auihi Turoa |\n"
"| 黄道 | Pito-o-Watea |\n"
"| 月亮 | Te Marama |\n"
"| 太阳 | Te Ra |\n"
"| Te-Ra-o-Tainui | 无对应欧洲星座的毛利星座，象征航海双体独木舟：猎户腰带为龙骨，毕星团为爪形帆，昴星团为船首。 |\n"
"\n"
"注：部分名称在不同部落或文献中可能有拼写或发音差异。"

