" - [#4]: [Romanian peasants beliefs in stars and sky – Translation of texts adapted from Ion Ottescu](http://www.sarm.ro/newsite/index.php?id=1&zi=29&luna=12&an=2009&act=news)\n"
" - [#5]: [PLANETARIUL BAIA MARE – MARAMURES](http://planetariubm.ro/)"
